OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Big and painful' cuts     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fneeded to fix budget - IFS 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The chancellor will need to make "big  
OL,6, and painful" spending cuts to put the  
OL,7, country's finances on a sustainable    
OL,8, path, the Institute for Fiscal Studies 
OL,9, think tank has warned.                 
OL,11,FWith a weaker economy and promised tax 
OL,12,Fcuts, there will be a large shortfall  
OL,13,Fin revenue, the IFS predicts.          
OL,15,FIt calculates the government would have
OL,16,Fto spend #60bn a year less by 2026-27. 
OL,18,FHowever, the Treasury said its tax cuts
OL,19,Fand reforms would deliver "sustainable 
OL,20,Ffunding for public services".          
